Full name: Andrea Hickethier | Location: Munich
Background: 20+ years in Marketing and Sales. + 6 Years in Leadership Roles in the Tech Consulting Industry. Best experience as a Leader so far: I led as a business person a Team of Software Developers and IT Service Specialists. Our common ground was the Customer Journey. Moreover we processed ISO 9001 and ISO 27001 successful . This experience influenced my and this is why I am since a couple of weeks a certified AI Security Manager in accordance to ISO 42001.
 🎯 Main Goals: Continuing my learning journey: Develop my Leadership further in the age of GenAI & Agents, manage my transformation as well as the transformation of the Revenue Engine in BtoB Organizations, improve my knowledge as non-tech person in using and understanding GenAI to create value and impact. 
Hobbies: Golfing and Cooking
Emoji I like: 🍑 
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrea-hickethier-65449aa0/
I feel so honored to be part of this community and I am looking forward to learn and contribute together with all of you!

**Full Name**: Georgi Pavlov 

**Background**: 25+ years mastering the skill of building the right solutions to real problems. Whether at a small startup, or contributing to open source, or working within a global tech giant—whether shaping developer experience or architecting one of the world’s largest e-commerce systems—I’ve built hands-on expertise across nearly every angle of IT: engineer, researcher, teacher, enterprise architect. These days, I am building the “brains” and the customer experience around a next-generation AI datacenter. 
**Role**: Senior Technology Leader | Advisor
**Location**: Sofia, Bulgaria 
**Hobbies**: I’m a curious traveler and nature lover. I love gardening and cooking (they don’t always love me back), get lost in history books, and find peace in music— my passion and stress ball. 

**LinkedIn**: https://www.linkedin.com/in/georgi-pavlov-0617741/ 

Thrilled to be joining as a **conversation leader**—looking forward to learning from each other and shaping an inspiring GenAI community together.
